theorem units_eq_one (u : «expr ˣ» ℕ) : u = 1 :=
  Units.ext <| nat.eq_one_of_dvd_one ⟨u.inv, u.val_inv.symm⟩
#align units_eq_one units_eq_one

is_unit_iff:
@[simp]
protected theorem is_unit_iff {n : ℕ} : is_unit n ↔ n = 1 :=
  iff.intro
    (fun ⟨u, hu⟩ =>
      match n, u, hu, Nat.units_eq_one u with
      | _, _, rfl, rfl => rfl)
    fun h => h.symm ▸ ⟨1, rfl⟩
#align is_unit_iff is_unit_iff
add_units_eq_zero:
theorem add_units_eq_zero (u : AddUnits ℕ) : u = 0 :=
  AddUnits.ext <| (nat.eq_zero_of_add_eq_zero u.val_neg).1
#align add_units_eq_zero add_units_eq_zero
